@{" Edit Palette     " link EDIT}  Information on current state of operation.
@{" Graphics Palette " link GRPH}  A preview of the selected graphic.
@{" Info Palette     " link INFO}  Not available.
@{" Texture Palette  " link TEXT}  List of all available graphics and the currently selected one..
